# Optional merge for `blusys build … qemu32` / `qemu32c3` / `qemu32s3`.
# If this file is empty or comment-only, the firmware uses the same Kconfig as the
# plain chip target; only the build directory differs (`build-qemu*` vs `build-esp32*`).
#
# Add CONFIG_* lines when you need QEMU-specific HAL (e.g. virtual framebuffer).
# See docs/app/cli-host-qemu.md for QEMU Kconfig merge notes.
# CLI matrix: docs/app/cli-host-qemu.md (in the blusys repo)
